introductionContent.text: This volume contains the abstracts for the tutorials presented at NAACL 2016.
Tutorials were selected by joint call for NAACL, ACL and EMNLP.
Together we accepted 6 NAACL tutorials out of a total of 32 joint submissions.

We would like to thank Kevin Knight (NAACL general chair), Jason Riesa (NAACL website chair), Adam Lopez and Margaret Mitchell (NAACL publications chairs), and Priscilla Rasmussen (local arrangement chair) for their help during the whole process.
We also want to extend our sincere gratitude to the other tutorial chairs who helped with reviewing: Rebecca Hwa, Bishan Yang, Alexandra Birch, and Willem Zuidema.
